data.description: MLS# 14657367 - Built by Altura Homes - Ready Now! ~ Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 2 car garage - 2 Story Townhome.. A welcome feeling as you enter into a large foyer which leads into the very open first level floor plan. This Includes family room, amazing kitchen with counter bar seating area and breakfast nook. Second story has two secondary bedrooms, large loft living space and full bath. Home completes with a Very spacious master suite with spa feel bath garden tub, separate shower, dual sinks and private water closet. You will have a vacation feel daily. Beautiful townhome located in Greenville, Texas
